                                                                                org.apache.hadoop.hbase.regionserver.HRegionServer notThisOne)
        Find regionserver other than the one passed. Can't rely on indexes into list of regionservers since crashed servers occupy an index.
        参数:
        cluster -
        notThisOne -
        返回:
        A regionserver that is not notThisOne or null if none found
